{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6f4a7cb230","title":"致彭德怀等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"387a9616d7","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":30,"articleId":"6f4a7cb230"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"56e83479df","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀等电！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6f4a7cb230"},{"id":"1bb731ce79","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月30日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6f4a7cb230"},{"id":"a5f1fc6f5d","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石以我军大部西渡，东岸所余不多，令胡宗南猛追。胡令周祥初、孔令恂两师向打拉池急进。关麟征师向靖远追击，毛炳文、王均部尾其后，似不会全部北进。何柱国令一骑兵师随胡军石翼相机追击。据以上情况，给我们打周、孔两师的极好机会。对周、孔右翼的骑兵师须以红二方面军有力部队拦阻之。红三十一军必须照彭令，由西向东打。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6f4a7cb230"},{"id":"66baa30ee1","type":"paragraph","text":"打拉池、西安州为我军尔后宁夏战役之屏障，万不可失，深望注意。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6f4a7cb230"},{"id":"eaff75ca2e","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和周恩来致彭德怀、贺龙、任强时、左权、最荣臻、徐海东、程子华并告朱德、张国秦电的主要内容。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6f4a7cb230"}],"page":{"id":"d2435ac870","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"6f4a7cb230","start":271,"end":271}}}},"__N_SSG":true}